title: Shoop Records, Vinyls 01 - 10 Kevceltic
description:
These are the first 10 vinyls released by Shoop and in my opinion are some of the best oldskool tunes ever - 

Shoop 01. QFX - Feel For Your Love 
Shoop 02. Bass X - Hardcore Disco 
Shoop 03. QFX - Phoebus EP 
Shoop 04. Aural 4 Play - Gotta Luv Me 
Shoop 05. Dance Overdose - Chemically Insane / Overdose Stomp 
Shoop 06. Massive - Heaven In Mind / Dansatak 
Shoop 07. Bass X - Atomic 
Shoop 08. Bass Reaction - Impulse 
Shoop 09. Massive - Key Of Life / Street Knowledge 
Shoop 10. Bass X - Base Xmas E.P 

If anyone has Shoop 028 - Mass Energy - Tempo Trauma and doesnt mind sharing let me know as its the only one I need. 

Cheers 
Kev
